<li id="cite_note-CCD-2">^ <a href="#cite_ref-CCD_2-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-CCD_2-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-CCD_2-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-CCD_2-3" title=""><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-CCD_2-4" title=""><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-CCD_2-5" title=""><sup><i><b>f</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-CCD_2-6" title=""><sup><i><b>g</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-CCD_2-7" title=""><sup><i><b>h</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-CCD_2-8" title=""><sup><i><b>i</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFMyers_SM.2C_Johnson_CP.2C_Council_on_Children_with_Disabilities2007">Myers SM, Johnson CP, Council on Children with Disabilities (2007). "<a href="http://pediatrics.aappublications.org/cgi/content/full/120/5/1162" class="external text" title="http://pediatrics.aappublications.org/cgi/content/full/120/5/1162" rel="nofollow">Management of children with autism spectrum disorders</a>". <i>Pediatrics</i> <b>120</b> (5): 1162–82. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1542%2Fpeds.2007-2362" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1542%2Fpeds.2007-2362" rel="nofollow">10.1542/peds.2007-2362</a></span>. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/17967921" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/17967921">PMID 17967921</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://pediatrics.aappublications.org/cgi/content/full/120/5/1162" class="external free" title="http://pediatrics.aappublications.org/cgi/content/full/120/5/1162" rel="nofollow">http://pediatrics.aappublications.org/cgi/content/full/120/5/1162</a></span>. <a href="http://aap.org/advocacy/releases/oct07autism.htm" class="external text" title="http://aap.org/advocacy/releases/oct07autism.htm" rel="nofollow">Lay summary