<li id="cite_note-Abrahams-3">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Abrahams_3-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Abrahams_3-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Abrahams_3-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Abrahams_3-3" title=""><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFAbrahams_BS.2C_Geschwind_DH2008">Abrahams BS, Geschwind DH (2008). "Advances in autism genetics: on the threshold of a new neurobiology". <i>Nat Rev Genet</i> <b>9</b> (5): 341–55. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1038%2Fnrg2346" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1038%2Fnrg2346" rel="nofollow">10.1038/nrg2346</a></span>. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18414403" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18414403">PMID 18414403</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Advances+in+autism+genetics%3A+on+the+threshold+of+a+new+neurobiology&amp;rft.jtitle=Nat+Rev+Genet&amp;rft.aulast=Abrahams+BS%2C+Geschwind+DH&amp;rft.au=Abrahams+BS%2C+Geschwind+DH&amp;rft.date=2008&amp;rft.volume=9&amp;rft.issue=5&amp;rft.pages=341%E2%80%9355&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1038%2Fnrg2346&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/18414403&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Autism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
