<li id="cite_note-149"><b><a href="#cite_ref-149" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREF.5B.5BHans_Asperger.7CAsperger_H.5D.5D1938"><a href="/wiki/Hans_Asperger" title="Hans Asperger">Asperger H</a> (1938). "Das psychisch abnormale Kind" (in German). <i>Wien Klin Wochenschr</i> <b>51</b>: 1314–7.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Das+psychisch+abnormale+Kind&amp;rft.jtitle=Wien+Klin+Wochenschr&amp;rft.aulast=%5B%5BHans+Asperger%7CAsperger+H%5D%5D&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BHans+Asperger%7CAsperger+H%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=1938&amp;rft.volume=51&amp;rft.pages=1314%E2%80%937&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Autism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-Lyons-150"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Lyons_150-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFLyons_V.2C_Fitzgerald_M2007">Lyons V, Fitzgerald M (2007). "<a href="http://springerlink.com/content/m55051670u35066p/fulltext.html" class="external text" title="http://springerlink.com/content/m55051670u35066p/fulltext.html" rel="nofollow">Asperger (1906–1980) and Kanner (1894–1981), the two pioneers of autism</a>". <i>J Autism Dev Disord</i> <b>37</b> (10): 2022–3. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1007%2Fs10803-007-0383-3" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1007%2Fs10803-007-0383-3" rel="nofollow">10.1007/s10803-007-0383-3</a></span>. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/17922179" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/17922179">PMID 17922179</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://springerlink.com/content/m55051670u35066p/fulltext.html" class="external free" title="http://springerlink.com/content/m55051670u35066p/fulltext.html" rel="nofollow">http://springerlink.com/content/m55051670u35066p/fulltext.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Asperger+%281906%E2%80%931980%29+and+Kanner+%281894%E2%80%931981%29%2C+the+two+pioneers+of+autism&amp;rft.jtitle=J+Autism+Dev+Disord&amp;rft.aulast=Lyons+V%2C+Fitzgerald+M&amp;rft.au=Lyons+V%2C+Fitzgerald+M&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.volume=37&amp;rft.issue=10&amp;rft.pages=2022%E2%80%933&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1007%2Fs10803-007-0383-3&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/17922179&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fspringerlink.com%2Fcontent%2Fm55051670u35066p%2Ffulltext.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Autism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-151"><b><a href="#cite_ref-151" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFFombonne_E2003">Fombonne E (2003). "<a href="http://ww1.cpa-apc.org:8080/Publications/Archives/CJP/2003/september/guesteditorial.asp" class="external text" title="http://ww1.cpa-apc.org:8080/Publications/Archives/CJP/2003/september/guesteditorial.asp" rel="nofollow">Modern views of autism</a>". <i>Can J Psychiatry</i> <b>48</b> (8): 503–5. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/14574825" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/14574825">PMID 14574825</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://ww1.cpa-apc.org:8080/Publications/Archives/CJP/2003/september/guesteditorial.asp" class="external free" title="http://ww1.cpa-apc.org:8080/Publications/Archives/CJP/2003/september/guesteditorial.asp" rel="nofollow">http://ww1.cpa-apc.org:8080/Publications/Archives/CJP/2003/september/guesteditorial.asp</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Modern+views+of+autism&amp;rft.jtitle=Can+J+Psychiatry&amp;rft.aulast=Fombonne+E&amp;rft.au=Fombonne+E&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft.volume=48&amp;rft.issue=8&amp;rft.pages=503%E2%80%935&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/14574825&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fww1.cpa-apc.org%3A8080%2FPublications%2FArchives%2FCJP%2F2003%2Fseptember%2Fguesteditorial.asp&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Autism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
